channel.title: Equip the item ID over 10000, and get item ID 9999?
channel.description: On my second source, Battlescape Blitz, when i equip an item whos ID is over 10000, it spawns a "shoe" (item 9999). Then i unequip the item, it is replaced my item 9999. What causes this is happen, and how can i fix it?
